<div class="heading-container">
<div class="layout wcl-ck-left-pane">
<div class="heading"><h2>Interested in Writing for the Brief?</h2> <p>Students from American University Washington College of Law have the opportunity to write for the <em>Human Rights Brief</em> by joining its staff.  Practitioners, scholars, and other students are invited to submit pieces on a variety of human rights and humanitarian law topics at any time.  Click below to learn more. </p>
